title: Wildcat Audubon Society to meet on Nov. 17
title_page: Wildcat Audubon Society to meet on Nov. 17
maintext: SCOTTSBLUFF - The Wildcat Audubon Society will be holding a regular meeting on Saturday, Nov. 17 at 7:30 p.m. The meeting will be held in the Conference Room of the South Plaza at Regional West Medical Center. Local beekeeper Ernest Griffiths will make a presentation on beekeeping in Western Nebraska. The meeting is open to the public. For information contact Alice Kenitz at 308-436-2959 or Tim Lane at 308-586-1277.
